h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks  [Budget|guide:renderBudgetMenu] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Budget Line Item" link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Budget Line Item" Report|guide:ShowForBudgetActionService].
* Enter valid input.
* Click "PDF" icon.
* System will show confirmation message of download.
* Actor clicks "Ok" button.
* Download "Budget Line Item" Report in PDF Format.

